---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — JADED DESIGN">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 px-8 py-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-jaded-bg/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/5">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="Dragon" class="w-10 h-10" />
      <span class="text-xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">
        <span class="text-dusty-pink">JADED</span>
        <span class="text-muted-sage"> × </span>
        <span class="text-cream">TylahJade</span>
      </span>
    </a>
    <div class="flex gap-8 text-sm text-muted-silver">
      <a href="/design" class="text-dusty-pink">Design</a>
      <a href="/art" class="hover:text-dusty-pink transition-colors">Art</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="min-h-[70vh] flex items-center px-6 pt-32 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-jaded-bg via-charcoal to-jaded-surface/50"></div>
      <div class="absolute w-80 h-80 bg-dusty-pink/5 rounded-full blur-3xl top-20 right-20"></div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl relative z-10">
        <p class="text-dusty-pink text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6">The Digital Hemisphere</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
          <span class="text-cream">Built with</span>
          <span class="text-dusty-pink"> precision.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-muted-silver text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          JADED DESIGN is the structured, strategic side of the creative mind — where ideas become sleek digital experiences that feel intentional at every touchpoint.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-cream/40 uppercase mb-12">The Approach</h2>
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-dusty-pink">Intention Over Accident</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed text-lg">
              Every decision — from color to kerning to the curve of a button — is deliberate. We don't decorate; we communicate. The result is design that feels effortless because every element has earned its place.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-dusty-pink">Strategy Before pixels</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed text-lg">
              Beautiful work that doesn't serve a purpose is decoration. We start every project by understanding the problem — then we design the solution. Branding without strategy is just logo-making.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-dusty-pink">Craft That Endures</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed text-lg">
              Trends come and go. We build visual systems that scale, websites that perform, and brands that last. Our work is designed to age gracefully — not just look good for the launch moment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-jaded-surface/30">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-cream/40 uppercase mb-12">The Designer Behind JADED</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-dusty-pink/20 to-muted-sage/20 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-6xl opacity-20">👤</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Tylah</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed mb-6">
              A multidisciplinary designer with a background in visual communication, digital product design, and creative direction. Working at the intersection of strategy and aesthetics — building brands that are as intelligent as they are visually compelling.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed">
              Obsessed with the details that make the difference: the perfect amount of negative space, the typeface that shifts everything, the micro-interaction that makes someone smile. Design isn't just what it looks like — it's how it works, how it feels, how it remembers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 text-center border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-6 text-cream">Start a project</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-silver mb-10">Have something in mind? Let's talk about how we can bring it to life.</p>
        <a href="/design/work-with-us" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-dusty-pink text-charcoal font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-dusty-pink/90 transition-all">
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="Dragon" class="w-6 h-6" />
          <span class="text-sm text-muted-silver">
            <span class="text-dusty-pink">JADED</span>
            <span class="text-muted-sage"> × </span>
            <span class="text-cream">TylahJade</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-silver text-xs">© 2025 JADED DESIGN. All rights reserved.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-6 text-xs text-muted-silver">
          <a href="/design" class="hover:text-dusty-pink transition-colors">Work</a>
          <a href="/design/about" class="hover:text-dusty-pink transition-colors">About</a>
          <a href="/design/work-with-us" class="hover:text-dusty-pink transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>